title: Knockout
description: The third and final book in The Halder Brothers series. Dylan's been through hell and back, but she's started building a life with Seb, Connor, and Gray. What happens when someone she doesn't remember from her past walks back into her life?Dylan's not sure she can take all the emotional exhaustion. But with the Halder brothers by her side, and on top of her, she can get through anything. It's time to finally get the answers she's been looking for her entire life. The only question is, can she stay safe while looking for those answers?Knockout is a reverse harem novel.
